{{Infobox person | name = Chaira Borderslee | native_name_lang = nl | birth_date = {{birth year and age|1975}} | birth_place = Netherlands | nationality = Dutch | occupation = {{hlist|Singer|actress|dancer}} }} '''Chaira Borderslee''' (born 1975, in Alkmaar) is a Dutch singer, actress and dancer.
==Biography== Borderslee started singing on when she was five. She sang in the Antillean children's choir Zjozjoli, in which they made albums and children's films. She studied at the Nel Roos Ballet Academy and then followed the premiere and higher professional education training Showmusical at the Amsterdam Dance Academy Lucia Marthas. She grew up in [[Heiloo]].
During her pre-tertiary education, Borderslee was seen as a singer and dancer in many well-known television programmes such as ''[[The Voice of Holland]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nu.nl/achterklap/2601696/chaira-borderslee-krijgt-boete.html|title=Chaira Borderslee krijgt boete|language=nr|publisher=Nu|date=29 Aug 2011|accessdate=3 Jul 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nu.nl/achterklap/2607027/chaira-borderslee-wil-boete-the-voice-niet-betalen.html|title=Chaira Borderslee wil boete The Voice niet betalen|language=nl|publisher=Nu|date=5 Sep 2011|accessdate=3 Jul 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraaf.nl/prive/20821978/__Chaira_geeft_niet_op__.html|title=Chaira Borderslee krijgt boete The Voice’|work=Privé|language=nl|publisher=Telegraaf.nl|date=22 Sep 2011|accessdate=3 Jul 2017}}</ref> and ''The Next Pop Talent'',<ref>{{cite web|url=http://zappen.blog.nl/talpa/2013/02/28/loslippige-chaira-borderslee-nu-in-the-next-pop-talent|title=Loslippige Chaira Borderslee nu in The Next Pop Talent|language=nl|publisher=Zappen|date=28 Feb 2013|accessdate=3 Jul 2017}}</ref> by Joop van den Ende and John de Mol,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraaf.nl/prive/20196812/__John_niet_boos_op_Chaira__.html|title=John de Mol: 'Chaira Borderslee is een prima vrouw'|work=Privé|language=nl|publisher=Telegraaf.nl|date=23 Sep 2011|accessdate=3 Jul 2017}}</ref> in which she performed with celebrities like [[Barry White]]. In addition to her high school education, Borderslee also performed vocal studio work on the R&B duo Unknown. Later she was asked to sing at the Dutch-language R&B project Vogelvrij. With this ensemble they recorded an album, two singles and two video clips.
In her graduation year, she made the transition to musical and played in, among others, ''West Side Story'',<ref name="rtl">{{cite web|url=https://www.rtlnieuws.nl/boulevard/entertainment/musicalster-chaira-borderslee-weer-vrijgezel|title=Musicalster Chaira Borderslee weer vrijgezel|language=nl|publisher=RTL Nieuws|date=24 May 2015|accessdate=3 Jul 2017}}</ref><ref name="prive">{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraaf.nl/prive/27170061/__Chaira___Dromen_waren_luchtkastelen____.html|title=Chaira: ’Dromen waren luchtkastelen…’|work=Privé|language=nl|publisher=Telegraaf.nl|date=6 Dec 2016|accessdate=3 Jul 2017}}</ref> ''Miss Saigon'',<ref name="rtl"/><ref name="prive"/> ''Fame'', ''Aida'',<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraaf.nl/prive/20182872/__Sprookje_voorbij_voor_Chaira__.html|title=Sprookje voorbij voor Chaira Borderslee|work=Privé|language=nl|publisher=Telegraaf.nl|date=27 Jul 2011|accessdate=3 Jul 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rtlnieuws.nl/boulevard/entertainment/chaira-borderslee-bijna-dakloos-door-ex|title=Chaira Borderslee bijna dakloos door ex|language=nl|publisher=RTL Nieuws|date=30 Jul 2013|accessdate=3 Jul 2017}}</ref><ref name="prive"/> ''Hair'' and ''Tarzan''.<ref name="rtl"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraaf.nl/prive/20645487/__Nieuwe_klap_voor_musicalster_Chaira_Borderslee__.html|title=Nieuwe klap voor musicalster Chaira Borderslee|work=Privé|language=nl|publisher=Telegraaf.nl|date=23 Jul 2008|accessdate=3 Jul 2017}}</ref><ref name="prive"/> In ''Aida'' and ''Hair'' she performed key roles.
In 2017 she became a naked partner in the celebrity version of ''[[Adam Zkt. Eva]]''.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.televizier.nl/categorie/amusement/chaira-borderslee-gelukkig-met-andere-adam.2472349.lynkx|title=Chaira Borderslee gelukkig met andere 'Adam'|work=Televizier.nl|language=nl|date=11 Jun 2017|accessdate=3 Jul 2017}}</ref>
